value.name: Living Wild: How To Change Your LIfe
value.original_name: Living Wild: How To Change Your LIfe
value.overview: Presenter Sophie Morgan suffered a spinal cord injury when she was 18 and is paralysed from the waist down. A difficult pandemic for everyone was worse for her, so here, looking at changes she could make to her lifestyle, she takes a trip around Britain meeting people who built new lives around the things they love.
